!## XBIFF {{{1
XBiff*volume: 80
XBiff*flip: false
XBiff*updates: 10
XBiff*fullPixmap: mailfull
XBiff*fullPixmapMask: mailfullmsk
XBiff*emptyPixmap: mailempty
XBiff*emptyPixmapMask: mailemptymsk
!XBiff*shapeWindow: true

